PrecisAppointment of WILFARD ADAM, of Burns Lake, British Columbia, as a British Columbia Treaty Commissioner, as nominated by the First Nations Summit, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective April 25, 1995, and ending on the earlier of April 24, 1997 or the date on which the appointment is revoked by resolution of the Summit.
